Description:
Refactor and add Docker-related scripts in package.json to simplify containerized development workflow. Include commands for starting containers, stopping services, viewing logs, restarting backend service, and running Prisma migration/status commands inside Docker containers. This will improve developer experience by reducing repetitive manual Docker commands and standardizing project setup commands.

{
  "scripts": {
    "docker:up": "docker compose up -d --build",
    "docker:down": "docker compose down",
    "docker:logs": "docker compose logs -f backend",
    "docker:restart": "docker compose restart backend",
    "prisma:migrate": "docker compose exec backend npx prisma migrate dev",
    "prisma:status": "docker compose exec backend npx prisma migrate status"
  }
}
